 font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Despite advances in cancer treatment, over 600,000 individuals die each year from cancer, among which 70% are expected to have pain as an anachronic symptom at the end of life: as per reported data in the literature.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Ever gold standard of end‐of‐life care is pain relief so that suffering individuals at the end can have a peaceful last phase of life.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">I understand as human and Medico that the continued challenge for optimum pain relief rests on communication being a key that can enable us to cross all barriers and challenges for pain management associated with cancer.</span></p>\r\n                                <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Following are some tips for communicating that help Pain Management In Cancer Patients</span></h2>\r\n                                <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Share your feelings.</span></h3>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Talking about your emotions might be hard, but it can comfort you and the people who care about you. When you tell someone whom you love what you&rsquo;re feeling, you give that person a chance to support you. You also give your relationship with that person a chance to grow. For some people, talking to others who are in a similar situation can help to decrease feelings of anxiety, isolation, or fear.</span></p>\r\n                                <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Be specific.</span></h3>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">When reaching out to others, be specific about the kind of support you need. Saying something like, &ldquo;It would be helpful if you could shop for groceries this week,&rdquo; or &ldquo;Can you please drive me to my next appointment?&rdquo; gives people a clear way to help. This approach cuts down on frustration and reassures your family and friends that they are being helpful.</span></p>\r\n                                <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Take steps to look and feel your best.</span></h3>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Many feel uncomfortable with their appearance after having surgery or chemotherapy. If you had breast surgery or are experiencing hair loss and changes in your physical appearance, learn about options available, such as breast prostheses and wigs. Give yourself time to adjust to changes, and try different solutions until you find what makes you feel most comfortable. Let yourself feel loved and cared&nbsp;for.</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">After a lumpectomy or mastectomy, a woman may find that regular activities, such as dressing, undressing, bathing, or being intimate with her partner or spouse, give rise to complex emotions. Some women feel so different that they stop taking care of their</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">emotional and physical needs. For example, a woman may distance herself emotionally from her partner. You can make other choices, such as choosing to remain close to your partner or spouse. Everyone deserves to feel loved and cared for. taking care of your well-being Regular physical activity has many health benefits, but it can also help improve your mood and reduce anxiety and depression</span></p>\r\n                                <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Talk to your spouse or partner</span></h3>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">About the physical closeness you need. Share how you feel about your body, and talk about what you think or worry that your partner is</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">feeling. Whatever your needs are &ndash; whether you feel a need for physical activity, or if you are not yet interested in being physically</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">intimate &ndash; let your partner know. Your partner is most likely waiting for your signal to know</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">what to do, how to act, and what you need. Discuss your concerns with your doctor or nurse. If you feel you have lost the desire to be</span></p>\r\n                                <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">physically intimate, bring it up with your doctor or nurse. These healthcare professionals can help you understand the physical changes that may be causing these feelings. They can also suggest ways to increase your interest in physical intimacy and make</span></p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'pain-management', '2021-02-05');
